Package com.djrapitops.plugin.api Description

Various static utilities that could not be moved.

This package mainly contains old deprecated code that uses static invocation that lead to memory leaks, leading to their deprecation.

Non deprecated classes:

See Also:
Check, TimeAmount, UUIDFetcher, Version
